  <a:documentation xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <p>Domain integrations that are common to all DITA for Publishers
    topic types.</p>
    <p>Note that this use of a separate module file just for domain integrations
    is not provided for in the DITA RELAX NG coding conventions. However, it is 
    a significant convenience for such a large number of topic types and does not
    violate the general DITA principles of modularity. The use of this module
    can always be replaced by simply copying these declarations into each
    document type shell grammar in place of the reference to this module.</p>
  </a:documentation>
  
